tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE patient_feedback (
  feedback_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id UUID NOT NULL,
  consultation_date DATE,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  satisfaction_rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE consultation_reports (
  report_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  consultation_id UUID NOT NULL,
  report_date DATE,
  report_text TEXT,
  improvement_actions TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE patient_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    doctor_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE PatientFeedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    consultation_date DATE,
    satisfaction_rating INT,
    feedback_text TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE PatientDetails (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(50),
    patient_age INT,
    patient_gender VARCHAR(10),
    patient_phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE TelehealthConsultation (
    consultation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    consultation_date DATE,
    consultation_type VARCHAR(20),
    consultation_duration INT
);

CREATE TABLE FeedbackReport (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    consultation_id INT,
    feedback_id INT,
    report_date DATE,
    report_text TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE patient_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT NOT NULL,
    rating FLOAT NOT NULL,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    consultation_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE patient (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    dob DATE,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE telehealth_consultation (
    consultation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT NOT NULL,
    consultation_date TIMESTAMP,
    consultation_duration INT,
    diagnosis TEXT,
    consultation_notes TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE healthcare_provider (
    provider_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    provider_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    specialization VARCHAR(50),
    location VARCHAR(100),
    contact_number VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE satisfaction_ratings (
    rating_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    consultation_id INT NOT NULL,
    provider_id INT NOT NULL,
    patient_id INT NOT NULL,
    rating_value FLOAT NOT NULL,
    feedback_text TEXT
)
